WEBVTT

00:00:00.599 --> 00:00:09.269
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:13.316 --> 00:00:23.786
Reverence for religion is natural, and
when a human being delves into religion

00:00:25.734 --> 00:00:36.664
so, very often, he begins to feel that for
thousands of years our parents and everyone
else have been discussing(talking about) religion,

00:00:36.664 --> 00:00:41.505
they kept on talking about Shri Ram and Shri
Krishna, and continued going to temples;

00:00:41.505 --> 00:00:47.529
why haven't we found peace even after
doing everything religiously?

00:00:48.345 --> 00:00:59.805
And whatever has been described that we
should get our Self realization, why
have we not achieved it?

00:01:01.001 --> 00:01:08.421
Especially after coming to this country, you
must have observed that your children will
start asking questions

00:01:08.421 --> 00:01:12.733
that after all, you keep on saying God—God,
where does that God even reside?

00:01:12.733 --> 00:01:15.573
Who is He, and how are we related to Him?

00:01:15.573 --> 00:01:22.831
I see a huge crisis ahead for you.

00:01:23.168 --> 00:01:32.528
Because you currently believe in religion according
to your tradition, are walking on the path of
righteousness and have faith in religion,

00:01:33.269 --> 00:01:46.169
but unless you can give this feeling, this
experience to your children, they will not
listen to you.

00:01:46.552 --> 00:01:55.542
Because you know, there's more independence here
than required between both children and adults.

00:01:55.542 --> 00:02:01.687
And here, there's also a huge risk of being
carried away by that freedom. It's not so
much in our own country.

00:02:01.687 --> 00:02:11.792
Therefore, I think that it's important for
every Indian, who has moved abroad, to get
to the basic principle of religion.

00:02:12.656 --> 00:02:19.866
If we do not achieve the basic principle
of religion, we too will remain incomplete.

00:02:20.277 --> 00:02:28.467
Just as no one can get to the essence
of religion merely by reading books

00:02:28.479 --> 00:02:35.169
and not only that, he cannot even receive
this All-Pervading power of God.

00:02:35.169 --> 00:02:41.114
There must be experience for that, and
until you have the experience of
Self-realization,

00:02:41.114 --> 00:02:43.063
you won't even enjoy religion.

00:02:43.063 --> 00:02:52.688
Just like, until your connection is established,
no matter how much you try to make a call,
who is going to hear you?

00:02:52.688 --> 00:02:58.239
Similarly, without having a connection with
God, without having a union with God,

00:02:58.856 --> 00:03:04.146
who would even listen to your prayer?
Prayer does not reach there.

00:03:04.146 --> 00:03:09.915
Many people say to Me, "Mother, we are so
religious, yet there is sickness in our home."

00:03:09.915 --> 00:03:15.922
"We have so many problems in our house,
we believe in God so much, then why is
God angry with us?"

00:03:16.143 --> 00:03:23.573
He is not upset, but a connection(yoga)
should be established with Him.

00:03:23.573 --> 00:03:30.433
And we don't understand this thing, although
this work has been done the most in our country.

00:03:30.433 --> 00:03:35.163
Go anywhere - in Punjab, Guru Nanak
Sahib did it

00:03:35.163 --> 00:03:41.788
In your Gujarat, none other than
Lord Krishna Himself incarnated.

00:03:41.788 --> 00:03:45.740
But even after him, many people like
Narsi Bhagat etc. have done this work?

00:03:45.740 --> 00:03:52.488
Especially how great is the work of Vallabhacharya.
Vallabhacharya himself was a Self-realized person.

00:03:52.488 --> 00:03:56.298
But at that time he could not do this
work with others because

00:03:56.298 --> 00:04:02.482
it is possible that people may not be prepared
in a way that they could attain Self-realization.

00:04:03.192 --> 00:04:09.294
Attaining self-realization is like a boon
for us.

00:04:09.294 --> 00:04:14.184
This is an immense right we have been
given, which we are not using.

00:04:14.250 --> 00:04:20.400
Within us resides a power known as Kundalini;
awakening It, and attaining Self-realization

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:24.019
is a very simple thing. Not a difficult thing
at all.

00:04:24.019 --> 00:04:28.886
And you must be knowing that our Sahaja Yoga
work is going on in 40 countries.

00:04:28.886 --> 00:04:37.157
Today, here in London itself, there are
thousands of people who are Sahaja Yogis,
meaning they are Self-realized.

00:04:37.157 --> 00:04:42.446
They can cure people's illnesses, and they
can awaken people's Kundalini.

00:04:42.446 --> 00:04:48.182
And—and not only that—but what the ailment
is or isn't, they can tell even that.

00:04:48.182 --> 00:04:56.231
They can alleviate any kind of problem,
themselves they are very peace-loving
and have very sublime thoughts.

00:04:56.231 --> 00:05:01.098
These people—and quite a few of them
used to take drugs—all have given up
drugs and are now ready.

00:05:01.098 --> 00:05:03.509
Used to drink alcohol, but have given
up and got ready.

00:05:03.509 --> 00:05:08.798
I never told them not to do this or that
– these things happen on their own.

00:05:08.798 --> 00:05:14.706
And in this country, there are many other
such diseases that can afflict us

00:05:14.706 --> 00:05:19.359
therefore, it's very important for us to
be cautious and to know that unless we

00:05:19.359 --> 00:05:24.414
attain Self-realization, we cannot even
know what ailment is afflicting us.

00:05:24.414 --> 00:05:30.421
This method of Self-realization is very
spontaneous and simple and is attainable
by everyone.

00:05:30.421 --> 00:05:35.602
But, "Those who seek, find"—one must
possess the power to seek.

00:05:35.602 --> 00:05:39.359
If you are not seeking it, no one can
forcibly impose it upon you.

00:05:39.359 --> 00:05:44.704
If you are seeking only money,
then you will certainly find money

00:05:44.704 --> 00:05:53.436
but if you want your inner strength, your
inner peace, your inner joy, and absolutely

00:05:53.436 --> 00:05:59.828
wish to embrace a truly beautiful life,
then you must attain Self-realization.

00:05:59.828 --> 00:06:04.481
For that, you needn't go into the forest;
you needn't renounce the world,

00:06:04.481 --> 00:06:10.575
no need to wear strange clothes; no need
to sell books—nothing at all.

00:06:10.575 --> 00:06:18.032
All of this is within you, it awakens, and
through that, firstly many diseases are cured,

00:06:18.032 --> 00:06:24.660
you attain mental peace, and furthermore,
you yourself become powerful.

00:06:24.660 --> 00:06:31.053
Now, the people who are singing here—the second
song you heard was composed by these people,
in Hindi language.

00:06:31.053 --> 00:06:37.666
Earlier you knew that if you had to teach
these Englishmen a line in Hindi,

00:06:37.666 --> 00:06:41.955
then one had to really rack one's brains.
Even then what they would say, God knows.

00:06:41.955 --> 00:06:49.111
And now, they will recite for you, in Sanskrit,
the entire composition by Adi Shankaracharya,
fluently and flawlessly.

00:06:49.111 --> 00:06:54.068
Actually, they are still back there—haven't
arrived yet, the ones who sing the songs,
so it took a little extra time.

00:06:54.068 --> 00:07:00.162
But you will be surprised that the people
who didn't know a single letter, today

00:07:00.162 --> 00:07:04.891
have begun writing poems in your Hindi
language, and they have memorized all the
recitations of Sanskrit.

00:07:04.891 --> 00:07:07.675
They sing in a witness manner, sing beautifully.

00:07:07.675 --> 00:07:15.591
The reason for this is that their Spirit has
been awakened. As soon as the Spirit awakens,
man awakens in many dimensions.

00:07:15.591 --> 00:07:20.211
And he starts thinking many different things
that he never thought before.

00:07:20.211 --> 00:07:23.201
For example, now there are some children who
are very weak in reading and writing,

00:07:23.201 --> 00:07:26.299
now, if they come into Sahaja Yoga, they
will come first in their class.

00:07:28.024 --> 00:07:31.365
Well, then, if there's a child whose
health isn't alright,

00:07:31.365 --> 00:07:34.370
bring him into Sahaja Yoga, he will himself
get better.

00:07:34.370 --> 00:07:38.884
Don't have to do anything special to make
it happen. Some have bad habits, some
have quarrels -

00:07:38.884 --> 00:07:43.356
Now many of these people are married to
Indians and also to foreigners,

00:07:43.358 --> 00:07:47.108
There have been international marriages as well,
but among us, conflicts are very rare.

00:07:47.108 --> 00:07:51.351
No one ever quarrels. Everyone lives together
with great love and joy.

00:07:51.351 --> 00:07:56.545
And the other negative aspect of this place,
immorality, is completely absent in these people.

00:07:56.545 --> 00:08:02.917
Just look how much, how much innocence
there is in their eyes.

00:08:02.917 --> 00:08:07.769
They don't have it in them to look at this
woman, look at that woman, look at this
man, look at that man - nothing.

00:08:07.769 --> 00:08:12.569
None of these things remain within them.
All of this has happened and have become
so pure – how did this happen?

00:08:12.569 --> 00:08:18.194
This is through Sahaja Yoga. But the quest
that exists in these people—that is not
found among Indians.

00:08:18.194 --> 00:08:23.116
I would say, among the Indians living abroad—
In India, there is much, there is a great
deal of search.

00:08:23.116 --> 00:08:28.467
People in India now—like in Bombay—if I
have a program,

00:08:28.467 --> 00:08:33.396
then, no fewer than fourteen thousand
people even come, even in Delhi, no fewer
than twelve thousand come.

00:08:33.396 --> 00:08:38.902
And if I'm in Noida etc, sixteen thousand people
turn up. When I visit the villages, people keep
coming in thousands.

00:08:38.902 --> 00:08:43.018
When I went to Russia—in Russia, there were
fourteen thousand, fifteen thousand people -

00:08:43.018 --> 00:08:47.562
The scientists and doctors from that place
all came forward and asked, "Well, what's
this? Grant us self-realization."

00:08:47.562 --> 00:08:50.808
But we are asleep. While sleeping we think -

00:08:50.808 --> 00:08:54.942
"Alright, we’ve taken God’s name twice,
offered our salutations—the job is done."

00:08:56.829 --> 00:09:04.159
Just like when some are sitting for 'Akhand Path'
(continuous recitation), one person starts singing
from here to there until they finish; then another
person places their finger down and takes over.

00:09:04.159 --> 00:09:07.938
What are you reading? You should know what's
written in it.

00:09:07.938 --> 00:09:14.073
Now, let me share a point with you regarding Sri
Krishna: that even to read Sri Krishna's Gita,
Self-realization is required.

00:09:14.073 --> 00:09:17.227
They read the Gita from morning till evening.
Does it have any effect?

00:09:17.227 --> 00:09:22.716
Whether one is a Hindu, a Muslim, or a Christian—
regardless of their caste— one is capable of
committing any kind of sin.

00:09:22.716 --> 00:09:25.232
There are no restrictions upon him. However,
a Sahaja Yogi will not do it.

00:09:25.232 --> 00:09:30.513
A Sahaja Yogi will never commit a sin, nor
perform any wrong deed, nor look upon
anything with a wrong perspective.

00:09:30.513 --> 00:09:33.828
What has happened? The light of the Spirit
has entered within.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:38.940
And as soon as this light of the Spirit
enters within, we become so pure.

00:09:38.940 --> 00:09:43.057
And all of this is your very own power—
the power residing within you.

00:09:43.057 --> 00:09:47.402
For this, you do not have to go anywhere outside,
ask anyone for anything—nothing at all.

00:09:47.402 --> 00:09:50.753
This is your own property, which you have
to acquire.

00:09:50.753 --> 00:09:57.858
And for that, I feel so strongly that this
is India's heritage, this is our heritage.

00:09:57.858 --> 00:10:02.998
And we should not lose this; we should
attain it—it happens very easily.

00:10:02.998 --> 00:10:07.784
But just as our freedom was easily accessible,
we didn't care about it,

00:10:07.784 --> 00:10:11.594
in the same way, we too when we attain
Sahaja Yoga, we do not value it.

00:10:11.594 --> 00:10:17.095
I too have given realization even to thousands
of Indians abroad, but they do not settle in
like these people.

00:10:17.095 --> 00:10:22.276
They do not grow into trees—they simply
remain small, just like dwarfs. What's
the reason can't understand.

00:10:22.276 --> 00:10:28.237
Because this Sahaja Yoga, when it is meant
to fulfill you with all kinds of joys,

00:10:28.237 --> 00:10:33.672
you are going to be perfect in every way, when
you will have all the facilities you need,

00:10:33.672 --> 00:10:38.474
you will be respected in every way, then
why not achieve this Sahaja Yoga?

00:10:38.474 --> 00:10:43.719
Now, it will take a lot of time to explain
what Sahaja Yoga is -

00:10:43.719 --> 00:10:52.603
and 'Sahaj'—meaning that which is born with
you—this right to Yoga resides within all
of you, and you must attain it.

00:10:52.603 --> 00:10:57.397
Kundalini resides within you—everyone has
already told you that the power of
Kundalini lies within you.

00:10:57.397 --> 00:11:01.371
You should awaken It, and you will be
benefitted by It's awakening.

00:11:01.371 --> 00:11:07.193
But those who say that awakening of the
Kundalini will cause you harm, they are wrong.

00:11:07.193 --> 00:11:12.564
She is your mother. Does your mother cause
you pain when she gives birth to you?

00:11:12.564 --> 00:11:15.936
The poor thing suffers all the pain
herself and gives birth to you.

00:11:15.936 --> 00:11:19.934
Indians should understand this themselves
because we respect mother a lot.

00:11:19.934 --> 00:11:25.131
So this Mother which resides within you, does
not cause you any sorrow or suffering,

00:11:25.131 --> 00:11:30.484
and eagerly awaits for the day when
It will give you Self-Realization.

00:11:30.484 --> 00:11:34.781
And then you too will become a Narsi Bhagat,
you too will become a Tukaram,

00:11:34.781 --> 00:11:38.788
you too will become a Ramdas Swami, you
too will become a Vallabhacharya.

00:11:38.788 --> 00:11:41.924
Doing this is not a difficult task at
all, it's very easy.

00:11:41.924 --> 00:11:45.892
But if you do not have the desire within
you, this task cannot be accomplished.

00:11:45.892 --> 00:11:48.953
Because the power of Kundalini is pure desire.

00:11:48.953 --> 00:11:53.927
Every Indian should have this pure desire
in his heart because he knows about it.

00:11:53.927 --> 00:11:59.355
These people had not even heard the name of
Kundalini. They did not even know what
God was.

00:11:59.355 --> 00:12:05.787
When I went to Russia, there wasn't even
any religion there. But how these people
understood—I simply cannot comprehend.

00:12:05.787 --> 00:12:09.122
How they recognized, I just can't understand.

00:12:09.122 --> 00:12:14.431
Even if they have spent days wandering after
a dishonest person, then to they return.

00:12:14.431 --> 00:12:18.949
And many false people too come from our place,
many hypocrites come too—and they make money.

00:12:18.949 --> 00:12:26.305
Tell Me, which saint or ascetic ever
accepted money in the name of God?
I don't know of any such person.

00:12:26.305 --> 00:12:30.295
Did someone take money—did any saint or
sadhu take money from people?

00:12:30.295 --> 00:12:37.271
So why go after people who take money
from you and make a fool of you?

00:12:37.271 --> 00:12:43.164
You yourself awaken your power, receive
your light, and live in its bliss.

00:12:43.164 --> 00:12:48.358
Now, if we talk about awakening, it can
happen even today, even now, but what
will happen in the future?

00:12:48.358 --> 00:12:50.216
You people really don't settle down in future.

00:12:50.216 --> 00:12:56.802
Look at these people, have come here from
different places, and how good their state is.

00:12:56.802 --> 00:13:01.911
I cannot tell you that each one of them
has given realization to hundreds of people.

00:13:01.911 --> 00:13:06.647
When you have all these powers within
you, you couldn't realize your worth.

00:13:06.647 --> 00:13:11.351
You did not understand what you are.
You are not merely a human being—
you are an Indian.

00:13:11.351 --> 00:13:17.553
And within an Indian, this power has been
passed down through endless generations,
through many lifetimes.

00:13:17.553 --> 00:13:22.123
Has been going on since many births. And that
I observe that, somehow—I do not know how

00:13:22.123 --> 00:13:26.208
it is gradually dying out in these countries.
Here, no one cares about it at all.

00:13:26.208 --> 00:13:31.124
No one here actually gives it any thought;
they just go—sit in a few temples, sing a
song or two—and consider the job done.

00:13:31.124 --> 00:13:38.103
That is not the thing. You too should attain
Self-realization and you should think

00:13:38.103 --> 00:13:42.862
that this is our own thing, and we should
thrive and grow in it.

00:13:42.862 --> 00:13:49.921
The manner in which the people here have understood
Sahaja Yoga, it is My hope that we too, who are
Indians, will come to understand it.

00:13:49.921 --> 00:13:54.634
Here, amongst you, there must be so many
disciples of Vallabhacharya.

00:13:54.634 --> 00:13:59.981
There must be many people who believe in
Vallabhacharya. How many would be believing
in Narsi Bhagat too.

00:13:59.981 --> 00:14:06.160
But we, too, can become like them. The very
simple way is to achieve Self-realization.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:09.974
Simply by singing their hymns, we cannot
become like them.

00:14:10.324 --> 00:14:13.924
Will tell you what all people do in
the name of Shri Krishna.

00:14:13.924 --> 00:14:17.158
Now, for instance—standing on the roadside,
chanting 'Hare Rama, Hare Krishna'.

00:14:17.158 --> 00:14:21.712
and they dance strangely and make a mess.
What's the benefit of that?

00:14:22.010 --> 00:14:27.920
On the contrary, their throats get ruined;
They come to Me saying they have cancer.
They sell books.

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:32.017
Books Christians sell too—their Bible;
and these people sell their Gita.

00:14:32.017 --> 00:14:36.697
Did Shri Krishna ask to sell the Gita?
Why, He Himself is Kubera incarnate!

00:14:37.043 --> 00:14:45.733
He who filled Sudama's entire home with
opulence, His disciples are begging on
the streets?

00:14:45.733 --> 00:14:52.292
Tell Me, what greater slander can there be
for Shri Krishna, who Himself is Kubera.

00:14:52.292 --> 00:14:57.081
If you—if you really come under His
protective shelter...

00:14:57.081 --> 00:15:02.131
then you shouldn't have need for anything at all.
But that is not the case—that is not the case.

00:15:02.131 --> 00:15:09.185
Actually, we believe in Shri Krishna,
but we do not believe in what Shri
Krishna said.

00:15:09.185 --> 00:15:16.681
I will tell you a few small things about
Shri Krishna, which you will definitely
understand if you look at them minutely.

00:15:16.681 --> 00:15:22.750
As Sri Krishna stated earlier—that you ought
to be 'Sthitapragya' (of steady wisdom).
He had said this point beforehand.

00:15:22.750 --> 00:15:25.855
To be 'Sthitapragya' means to attain
Self-realization, it means Knowledge.

00:15:25.855 --> 00:15:31.289
Knowledge does not mean bookish knowledge;
but you should be able to feel in your hands.

00:15:31.289 --> 00:15:35.491
You should have a realization(experience)
of it. You ought to know

00:15:35.491 --> 00:15:39.566
that what is that power which pervades this
entire universe?

00:15:39.566 --> 00:15:44.737
You ought to know that, and for that Adi
Shankaracharya has said, 'Salilam Salilalam'.

00:15:44.737 --> 00:15:51.834
It means cool breeze, one should know about
it. This is what should be called Knowledge.

00:15:51.834 --> 00:15:59.501
Knowledge meant awareness. From this awareness
'bodh' that the word 'Veda' (Vid) is derived:
signifying that you ought to know.

00:15:59.501 --> 00:16:06.796
Even after knowing, then you can understand
why the first thing he said was, 'You know this.'

00:16:06.796 --> 00:16:11.089
But Arjuna said, "You speak of knowing;
then what becomes of action?"

00:16:11.089 --> 00:16:15.949
Even then, because Shri Krishna was a
great diplomat, He thought,

00:16:15.949 --> 00:16:20.255
"Nothing sinks into a human brain easily,"
so He thought of turning things around
and talk to them that way.

00:16:20.255 --> 00:16:24.859
But that's not the case anymore. I'm
a Mother, so I'll tell you everything
straight away.

00:16:24.859 --> 00:16:30.513
Shri Krishna thought, "To make a man understand
it's better to confuse him a little, then
he'll come around properly."

00:16:30.513 --> 00:16:36.219
So what He said to that was, "Perform your
duty(action), but leave that action upon God."

00:16:36.219 --> 00:16:41.198
That cannot happen at all. No matter what
we say—"We performed this action, and
left it to the Divine"—

00:16:41.198 --> 00:16:44.850
"I performed the deed and left it to the
Divine"—even if someone kills someone,
they'll say,

00:16:44.850 --> 00:16:47.205
"I committed murder and even left that to God."

00:16:47.205 --> 00:16:51.898
We simply cannot leave things to the Divine
—the reason being that ego is inherently
present within us.

00:16:52.136 --> 00:16:57.356
But when the ego breaks down upon Self-realization,
what do we say then?

00:16:57.356 --> 00:17:01.887
What do we say? "This is happening; this is
going on, this is taking shape(being made)."

00:17:01.887 --> 00:17:08.176
We do not say, "We are doing it; it is
being accomplished by us." This thing
has to be shattered.

00:17:08.176 --> 00:17:11.769
Then it happens that, "God is doing it, who
are we? We are merely standing in between."

00:17:11.769 --> 00:17:18.461
Then it is said in reality, from within—
only after knowing this; not merely in
a superficial manner

00:17:18.461 --> 00:17:24.361
that, 'It's the Supreme Being alone Who is
doing all of this.' And when one begins to
perceive things in this manner, one's
entire life becomes filled with miracles.

00:17:24.361 --> 00:17:30.498
So many miracles, so many miracles that you
will be astonished at what you truly are.

00:17:30.498 --> 00:17:34.011
What a great thing you are! You have absolutely
no idea what you truly are.

00:17:34.011 --> 00:17:40.343
For example, take your own television and
go to a small village in Gujarat,

00:17:40.343 --> 00:17:46.502
and if you tell them that there will be a
beautiful song in it and they would watch all
the drama, they won't believe it.

00:17:46.502 --> 00:17:51.090
But as soon as it's connection is established,
they'll say, "Oh wow, this is an amazing thing."

00:17:51.090 --> 00:17:55.505
Similarly, as soon as your connection is
established, you, too, will feel exactly
the same way

00:17:55.505 --> 00:17:58.946
that, "We are truly extraordinary; what
a magnificent thing we have attained."

00:17:58.946 --> 00:18:03.291
So, you must know how to value yourself.
The first thing is, you should value yourself

00:18:03.291 --> 00:18:09.157
and must realize that as an Indian, we have
behind us a tradition of immense magnitude.

00:18:09.157 --> 00:18:15.767
The second thing Shri Krishna said about this
is, "Do your duty but leave it to Me."
That cannot happen.

00:18:15.767 --> 00:18:20.222
Now, He said something very interesting regarding
devotion. For devotion He said that,

00:18:20.222 --> 00:18:25.827
"Whatever you offer Me, be it fruit or flower
—I will accept; if you offer water, I will
accept it." But what kind of devotion must
you practice? "Undivided(ananya)."

00:18:25.827 --> 00:18:29.637
Now, the meaning we generally ascribe to
'ananya bhakti'(exclusive devotion),
that is incorrect.

00:18:29.637 --> 00:18:32.366
'Ananya' means when there is not the other.

00:18:32.366 --> 00:18:37.309
Meaning, when we become one with God, when we
achieve theocrasy, devotion at that time,

00:18:37.309 --> 00:18:40.854
meaning, devotion is possible only when we
establish a connection with Him.

00:18:40.854 --> 00:18:45.070
And any devotion preceding that is merely
empty talk.

00:18:45.070 --> 00:18:50.674
And if you can grasp this point, that this
Shri Krishna explained with great method
and precision.

00:18:50.674 --> 00:18:54.106
Many people sing day and night, chanting
God's name,

00:18:54.106 --> 00:18:57.429
many people even chant the name of Shri Krishna
as many as 125,000 times.

00:18:57.429 --> 00:19:01.826
Their hands also get worn out. A lady came,
poor lady, she came to Me and said,

00:19:01.826 --> 00:19:05.864
"Mother, my hands are trembling," I said, "Why?
What kind of work do you do that your hands
are shaking?"

00:19:05.864 --> 00:19:08.817
She said, "Nothing, I just keep writing
the name of Shri Krishna."

00:19:08.817 --> 00:19:12.396
And that is the very finger of Shri Krishna—
that very finger began to tremble.

00:19:12.396 --> 00:19:17.850
I said, "Oh, why are you doing this? Just
taking the name of Shri Krishna once,
that's enough."

00:19:17.850 --> 00:19:23.199
"Why is there a need to take the name so many
times? Perhaps you have no connection with
Him at all, that's why you are shouting."

00:19:23.199 --> 00:19:29.652
And then there's also the thing that those
to whom we are not related—suppose that here
at the queen's place,

00:19:29.652 --> 00:19:33.833
if you go to her door and shout, "Hey Elizabeth!
Elizabeth!"—then the police of that place will
arrest you right there.

00:19:33.833 --> 00:19:38.130
The same thing happens that the police had
caught her that, "Be careful, there's no
need to overdo it."

00:19:38.130 --> 00:19:43.245
From this we should understand that this
is what we call an unauthorized attempt;
we do not have the right.

00:19:43.245 --> 00:19:48.261
Unless we have entered the kingdom of God,
what right do we have that we call Him,

00:19:48.261 --> 00:19:52.885
"Come on, You do this," we think God is
right there in our pocket. "Will You
do it or not?"

00:19:52.885 --> 00:19:58.507
Unless you enter His kingdom, you have
no right over Him.

00:19:58.507 --> 00:20:07.738
But upon entering His kingdom, you will be
astonished at the immense love with which
He cares for us every single moment.

00:20:07.738 --> 00:20:15.127
As was Sudama's condition - you have seen for
Sudama, when he was going in the wedding
procession along with Shri Krishna,

00:20:15.127 --> 00:20:21.739
he was showered upon with pearls. Sudama thought
to himself, "If only a single pearl would fall
into my lap as well."

00:20:22.680 --> 00:20:28.870
But when he went home, what he saw was that
his entire house was made of gold.

00:20:28.870 --> 00:20:37.899
He was Kubera. Such a great incarnation in
person resided in your Gujarat for so many
years and did such immense work.

00:20:38.738 --> 00:20:45.558
But the special thing about Him, that we didn't
adopt. And that special thing is this,

00:20:45.558 --> 00:20:53.119
that you should first attain your Self-realization.
And this is what Vallabhacharya also said,

00:20:53.119 --> 00:20:58.379
Narsi Bhagat, too, said this. All the saints
and sages who have been in our country
have said this.

00:20:58.379 --> 00:21:02.065
But nowadays, instead of saints and sages,
there are strange gurus and their distorted forms.

00:21:02.065 --> 00:21:04.726
They are making a lot of money and engaged
in all sorts of strange pursuits.

00:21:04.726 --> 00:21:10.346
Therefore, it behooves us - now that the
truth is being made available to us—to
achieve it and delve deeply into it.

00:21:10.346 --> 00:21:15.633
Now, we don't have such a center here,
but they were saying there's a very
good center in Hackney.

00:21:15.633 --> 00:21:19.529
People meet there. So, some people have
come over to our place

00:21:19.529 --> 00:21:22.305
and they are working very hard, and have
also achieved a great deal.

00:21:22.305 --> 00:21:26.629
And these people who have come from various
countries—they too, are all your brothers
and sisters.

00:21:26.629 --> 00:21:33.191
In their minds, there are no such distinctions,
no 'colored' or 'colorless'; none of these
notions even exist in their heads.

00:21:33.191 --> 00:21:39.605
They are such decent people. They are very
well educated; some are doctors, some are
architects, and so on.

00:21:39.605 --> 00:21:45.035
Some of them are professors, all very educated,
good people. Yet they are very humble.

00:21:45.035 --> 00:21:49.419
With such simplicity, they came and sat down
on the ground, and how much they consider
you their own.

00:21:49.419 --> 00:21:52.342
And they actually think that every single
Indian is a deity.

00:21:52.342 --> 00:21:55.501
They feel that every single person in India
is a deity.

00:21:55.501 --> 00:21:58.379
And every single woman in India is a goddess.

00:21:58.379 --> 00:22:01.392
This is how they look at you, and
they hold you in such high regard.

00:22:01.392 --> 00:22:04.043
This is somewhat true, because the tradition
is very big.

00:22:04.043 --> 00:22:07.310
Our passion is huge and we have achieved
a lot.

00:22:07.310 --> 00:22:10.907
But where do we know who we are?

00:22:10.907 --> 00:22:14.874
That is the only difference. If we
were to realize what we truly are,
it would be great.

00:22:14.874 --> 00:22:19.367
So, I just came today to say that now
you all should come to our centers

00:22:19.367 --> 00:22:21.480
and there you achieve this thing.

00:22:21.480 --> 00:22:25.685
Now, if you simply say that Mother we came
just to see You(for darshan), then all the
temples are there for darshan -

00:22:25.685 --> 00:22:31.612
What benefit was got from that? Every single
time, you people have gone for 'Darshan'
—you keep going year after year.

00:22:31.612 --> 00:22:35.294
You've already seen Mother many a times,
what good is that?

00:22:35.294 --> 00:22:38.074
There is no benefit in mere 'Darshan' now;
now attain it—it is a matter of attainment.

00:22:38.074 --> 00:22:43.197
You have your darshan. I wish for all of
you to behold your own true selves—and
it is truly beautiful.

00:22:43.197 --> 00:22:47.043
After that, everything becomes so beautiful
that you will be amazed.

00:22:47.043 --> 00:22:54.014
Any home where Sahaja Yoga once enters—
there resides peace, joy, happiness,
every form of well-being, and abundance.

00:22:54.014 --> 00:23:00.147
A truly beautiful atmosphere is created
for everything.

00:23:00.147 --> 00:23:04.410
I hope there will be quite a few people
here next time I'll come.

00:23:04.410 --> 00:23:08.696
I travel a lot, I'm going again, you know,
to Austria tomorrow morning.

00:23:08.696 --> 00:23:15.280
I have to leave at 9:30; I am constantly
traveling and have to roam all over
the world.

00:23:15.280 --> 00:23:21.275
But I want the Indian people here to
wake up to this matter.

00:23:21.275 --> 00:23:28.882
There are many things in our country that
we have completely forgotten, and that
is why all this mess happens.

00:23:28.882 --> 00:23:35.959
If we remember that we are Indians, and that
India is a vast and mighty land of Yoga—

00:23:35.959 --> 00:23:41.698
The entire world has its eyes fixed upon
you. Everyone is watching, seeing that the
people of this Land of Yoga have arrived.

00:23:41.698 --> 00:23:47.014
Just yesterday, a gentleman was telling Me,
"Mother, it’s a good thing these Indians
have arrived."

00:23:47.014 --> 00:23:50.813
I said, "Why?" He said, "A little bit of
our culture will be improved."

00:23:50.813 --> 00:23:54.477
"These people come here, our culture will
somewhat change."

00:23:54.477 --> 00:23:58.257
"We have no culture whatsoever; they have
come and will bestow culture upon us."

00:23:58.257 --> 00:24:03.773
But if we start learning their culture,
what will these poor things learn from us?

00:24:03.917 --> 00:24:09.857
So we have a lot to do here. You have
come to this country, God has specially
brought you here.

00:24:09.857 --> 00:24:14.209
So, you attain Self-realization and
establish yourself firmly in your place.

00:24:14.209 --> 00:24:18.668
And once you have settled in, you will
realize just how much work you have to
do in this country.

00:24:18.668 --> 00:24:20.969
And how much there is to be given to
these people?

00:24:20.969 --> 00:24:25.525
At first you know yourself—I bestow upon
you My infinite blessings.

00:24:25.525 --> 00:24:30.643
And I tell everyone, next time, please,
please do come and meet Me.

00:24:30.643 --> 00:24:35.653
And I would like to do whatever I can,
for all of you.
